N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6155.5 - Payment

State Regulations

Payment for publications, seminars, and other services
provided by the Bureau of Prosecution Services shall be made by government
check, government voucher, or attorney's check only, payable to the Division of

Criminal Justice Services. Notes
